content/uploads/2011/05/5713206060_3b5a20a4d5.jpg)](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/05/5713206060_3b5a20a4d5.jpg)[洛卡地震](http://www.flickr.com/photos/aperiago/5713206060/in/photostream/
